{\"id\":2,\"title\":\"Command in Python\.title: Homebrew
{\"id\":2,\"title\":\"Command in Python\.content:
For Mac Only
Install Homebrew
#/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"
#brew
#brew update
#brew list
#brew --version

Install Python
#brew install python
#brew upgrade python@3.10

Install Node Js
#brew install node
#node --version

Install pip
#brew install brew-pip

Install pipenv
#brew install pipenv
#pipenv shell

{\"id\":2,\"title\":\"Command in Python\.title: if-elif-else
{\"id\":2,\"title\":\"Command in Python\.content:
<-----if----->
a = 33
b = 200
if b > a:
  print("b is greater than a")
  
<-----if else----->
a = 200
b = 33
if b > a:
  print("b is greater than a")
else:
  print("b is not greater than a")

<-----if elif else----->
a = 200
b = 33
if b > a:
  print("b is greater than a")
elif a == b:
  print("a and b are equal")
else:
  print("a is greater than b")
